

LANGIS

   mantika, “aseyte”
   langis
   oil, grease

   langis
   unction

   langis (slang)
   money

   langis at tubig
   oil and water
   = people who don’t get along

   Langisan mo ito.
   Oil this. Put oil on this.

   Kailangan ng langis.
   Needs grease.

   A Spanish-derived word for ‘grease’ is grasa.
